A Voice Episode Forty_Two 08 December 2025
WEBVTT

00:00:28.131 --> 00:00:30.352
Back to the Ocean Studio here as part

00:00:30.391 --> 00:00:31.371
of the Yada Yahowah blog.

00:00:31.932 --> 00:00:34.253
Beautiful day overlooking the Caribbean

00:00:34.314 --> 00:00:34.594
Sea.

00:00:35.314 --> 00:00:38.234
We’re proceeding with what I call the

00:00:38.895 --> 00:00:40.115
Sixth on the Eighth.

00:00:41.095 --> 00:00:45.258
This is a series that is devoted to Dowd,

00:00:45.298 --> 00:00:48.018
through the voice of Dowd,

00:00:48.098 --> 00:00:51.200
who is David, the Son of God, the Messiah,

00:00:51.340 --> 00:00:52.881
our Savior, the returning King.

00:00:53.401 --> 00:00:55.082
He’s the one who was counterfeited to

00:00:55.121 --> 00:00:57.143
create the illusion of Jesus.

00:00:57.982 --> 00:01:00.204
He wrote a series of MizMowr,

00:01:00.225 --> 00:01:01.305
which we call Psalms,

00:01:01.847 --> 00:01:03.508
and one of them is the sixth.

00:01:04.069 --> 00:01:05.849
And in the opening lines of the sixth,

00:01:05.890 --> 00:01:07.912
we have already discovered that,

00:01:08.272 --> 00:01:08.873
first of all,

00:01:08.912 --> 00:01:11.575
this was written for the eighth

00:01:11.695 --> 00:01:12.075
octave.

00:01:12.771 --> 00:01:15.572
And the eighth octave is what we

00:01:15.673 --> 00:01:18.935
experience once God’s objectives with man

00:01:19.015 --> 00:01:19.896
are finally met.

00:01:21.096 --> 00:01:22.837
And to share that with you,

00:01:23.018 --> 00:01:24.558
it’s by recap.

00:01:25.179 --> 00:01:27.960
It has been just eight

00:01:28.001 --> 00:01:30.462
years shy now of six thousand years since

00:01:30.522 --> 00:01:33.545
we were escorted out of Gan ‘Eden for

00:01:33.665 --> 00:01:35.865
what I would call bad behavior.

00:01:37.406 --> 00:01:39.849
We showed no initiative in the Garden.

00:01:39.868 --> 00:01:40.450
Man didn’t.

00:01:41.510 --> 00:01:43.753
Us, represented by Adam and Chawah.

00:01:44.793 --> 00:01:45.795
We showed no initiative.

00:01:46.575 --> 00:01:48.537
Didn’t make any contribution of any kind.

00:01:49.078 --> 00:01:50.259
Unwilling to work with God.

00:01:51.004 --> 00:01:52.084
And that was a primary purpose.

00:01:52.103 --> 00:01:53.405
We were inobservant,

00:01:54.025 --> 00:01:56.344
unaware of what was happening around us

00:01:56.885 --> 00:02:00.225
and showed no indication that we wanted to

00:02:00.245 --> 00:02:03.546
be explorers and to learn about life and

00:02:03.566 --> 00:02:05.268
the very fabric of existence,

00:02:05.287 --> 00:02:06.668
which is something that God wanted to

00:02:06.688 --> 00:02:08.228
share with us.

00:02:08.548 --> 00:02:10.209
We were not good listeners.

00:02:10.568 --> 00:02:12.588
We were not responding to God.

00:02:13.069 --> 00:02:13.870
And worst of all,

00:02:13.909 --> 00:02:15.750
we showed that we couldn’t be trusted.

00:02:16.289 --> 00:02:18.170
All of those things did not bode well

00:02:18.211 --> 00:02:18.670
for the

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.360
conditions that were in the Garden, and God

00:02:21.381 --> 00:02:23.223
said, “Well, we’re going to draw this to

00:02:23.242 --> 00:02:25.865
a close.” It was God Himself who caused

00:02:25.925 --> 00:02:28.627
that time to end, and it was also

00:02:28.667 --> 00:02:30.247
so that we would have a chance over six

00:02:30.288 --> 00:02:32.530
thousand years to get our act together, to

00:02:32.610 --> 00:02:34.550
start listening to God, to start paying

00:02:34.591 --> 00:02:36.412
attention to what is actually happening

00:02:36.451 --> 00:02:39.014
around us, to be more observant—for example,

00:02:39.054 --> 00:02:41.756
to observe the fact that planet Earth

00:02:41.895 --> 00:02:42.497
is really

00:02:44.007 --> 00:02:46.587
a larger version of the microcosm that

00:02:46.647 --> 00:02:50.049
God created in ‘Eden. It was a protective

00:02:50.088 --> 00:02:52.509
and sheltered enclosure that was conducive

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:55.350
to life, and that is what our planet

00:02:55.411 --> 00:02:57.692
is. And this massive universe with two

00:02:57.752 --> 00:03:01.073
trillion galaxies, each averaging hundreds

00:03:01.112 --> 00:03:03.854
of billions of stars and those with

00:03:03.894 --> 00:03:06.675
countless planets and moons—Earth

00:03:06.735 --> 00:03:08.616
appears to be the only place that is

00:03:08.716 --> 00:03:11.637
actually finely tuned and protected

00:03:12.427 --> 00:03:14.936
for life—protected in the sense that it

00:03:14.996 --> 00:03:17.403
is our molten core of this planet that

00:03:17.444 --> 00:03:18.930
creates the protection with our magnetic field from

00:03:20.153 --> 00:03:22.555
cosmic rays and our atmosphere,

00:03:22.655 --> 00:03:24.556
particularly as it’s filled with water

00:03:24.917 --> 00:03:27.098
vapor, that also is a protective

00:03:27.138 --> 00:03:29.618
environment that made life on this planet

00:03:29.679 --> 00:03:33.281
possible. Perfect size planet, perfect size

00:03:33.341 --> 00:03:36.182
moon, perfectly positioned moon and planet

00:03:36.242 --> 00:03:39.364
together, perfect distance from the

00:03:39.383 --> 00:03:42.746
perfect kind of sun—all of which

00:03:42.846 --> 00:03:45.907
were necessary to create life along with

00:03:46.388 --> 00:03:48.429
our molten core,

00:03:48.490 --> 00:03:49.569
along with the tectonic plates,

00:03:49.650 --> 00:03:51.491
along with the tides that the moon

00:03:51.852 --> 00:03:53.633
provides,

00:03:53.673 --> 00:03:54.294
along with the angle on our axis,

00:03:54.354 --> 00:03:57.515
along with the size of our circular orbit

00:03:57.575 --> 00:04:00.377
around the sun—all of it

00:04:00.437 --> 00:04:03.080
is conducive to life, and without life

00:04:03.879 --> 00:04:07.703
can’t thrive, and with it life is prolific.

00:04:07.883 --> 00:04:10.604
And so our planet is exactly what God

00:04:11.224 --> 00:04:15.108
was trying to convey to us through the

00:04:15.147 --> 00:04:17.548
story of ‘Eden.

00:04:17.588 --> 00:04:19.411
And while ‘Eden was a bit like a

00:04:20.370 --> 00:04:23.692
man in a fishbowl, if you will,

00:04:24.312 --> 00:04:25.932
where we just never showed any interest in

00:04:26.572 --> 00:04:29.995
what was happening in that bowl or around

00:04:30.055 --> 00:04:33.216
us, didn’t much care for the One who was

00:04:33.315 --> 00:04:33.435
providing the nutrients in that bowl, we

00:04:34.406 --> 00:04:36.747
have now been released to the entire

00:04:36.786 --> 00:04:39.788
planet—man with a neshamah, with a

00:04:39.809 --> 00:04:41.569
conscience, who’s capable of figuring these

00:04:41.610 --> 00:04:44.331
things out. And here we are now six

00:04:44.391 --> 00:04:46.473
thousand years later, eight years shy of

00:04:46.492 --> 00:04:49.495
that, in year 2025

00:04:49.535 --> 00:04:51.975
becoming 2026. This all comes

00:04:52.016 --> 00:04:56.218
to a conclusion in 2033.

00:04:56.298 --> 00:04:58.519
Here we are now with this opportunity for

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.940
the first time to see the Earth as

00:05:00.980 --> 00:05:02.502
‘Eden,

00:05:03.084 --> 00:05:06.125
to understand that we failed the test that

00:05:06.165 --> 00:05:08.266
God had for us in ‘Eden because we

00:05:08.906 --> 00:05:09.206
were inobservant.

00:05:09.225 --> 00:05:12.726
We were not listening.

00:05:12.766 --> 00:05:15.348
We were inactive.

00:05:15.408 --> 00:05:17.309
We weren’t willing to engage and work with

00:05:17.468 --> 00:05:18.788
God to make

00:05:19.228 --> 00:05:20.589
life better here. And until we can show

00:05:20.670 --> 00:05:23.211
that we are willing to do those things

00:05:23.250 --> 00:05:23.831
and are reliable, dependable, God can’t take

00:05:24.870 --> 00:05:26.970
us off this planet and show us the

00:05:27.009 --> 00:05:28.810
rest of the universe that He’s created,

00:05:28.850 --> 00:05:31.471
take us beyond three dimensions into four,

00:05:31.511 --> 00:05:33.172
five, six, and ultimately seven dimensions,

00:05:33.232 --> 00:05:35.612
each with an infinite increase in

00:05:35.951 --> 00:05:38.853
possibilities and opportunities. All of

00:05:38.872 --> 00:05:41.514
that requires us to be really good

00:05:41.913 --> 00:05:44.194
listeners and to demonstrate that we’re

00:05:44.254 --> 00:05:47.495
trustworthy

00:05:47.514 --> 00:05:49.795
and that we’re interested in exploring.

00:05:49.814 --> 00:05:52.076
We’re observant individuals,

00:05:52.115 --> 00:05:52.615
desirous of all of this.

00:05:53.776 --> 00:05:55.459
And that is why we’re exploring God’s

00:05:55.499 --> 00:05:57.141
words.

00:05:57.221 --> 00:05:58.362
Now,

00:05:58.704 --> 00:06:00.766
as it relates to the sixth MizMowr in

00:06:00.786 --> 00:06:01.127
the eighth octave,

00:06:01.166 --> 00:06:01.326
I’ve said it’s been six thousand years,

00:06:01.767 --> 00:06:04.471
eight years shy of that now.

00:06:04.511 --> 00:06:05.531
And we are

00:06:05.612 --> 00:06:07.654
returned to the Garden from year six

00:06:07.694 --> 00:06:09.237
thousand to year seven thousand.

00:06:10.319 --> 00:06:11.040
And it’s during that time that there’s a

00:06:11.699 --> 00:06:14.262
number of us, eight in particular,

00:06:14.302 --> 00:06:16.043
plus Dowd and myself,

00:06:16.824 --> 00:06:20.028
that are responsible for helping mankind

00:06:20.108 --> 00:06:22.269
resolve the failures of ‘Eden and become

00:06:23.310 --> 00:06:24.831
worthy to earn God’s trust and become

00:06:24.851 --> 00:06:28.154
interesting to Yahowah.

00:06:29.896 --> 00:06:32.658
That’s a thousand-year period.

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:35.922
Takes us to year seven thousand, and

00:06:36.021 --> 00:06:37.202
between seven thousand and on into the

00:06:38.714 --> 00:06:39.995
eighth octave.

00:06:40.016 --> 00:06:42.098
Those who pass that test,

00:06:42.137 --> 00:06:45.079
who show that they can be trusted,

00:06:45.220 --> 00:06:46.100
who are interesting, who listen to God,

00:06:47.081 --> 00:06:48.583
who are responsive to Him,

00:06:49.242 --> 00:06:50.663
who, when knocked down, know how to get

00:06:50.684 --> 00:06:52.665
back up,

00:06:52.706 --> 00:06:54.507
who are engaged and want to make a

00:06:54.846 --> 00:06:57.649
contribution—those people are going to be

00:06:57.689 --> 00:06:58.110
involved,

00:06:58.149 --> 00:06:59.951
allowed off of this planet and into

00:07:00.011 --> 00:07:00.732
dimensions, including time,

00:07:00.771 --> 00:07:02.052
such that we can go off and explore

00:07:02.293 --> 00:07:05.295
this universe with Yahowah.

00:07:05.896 --> 00:07:07.778
And so that’s why this is in the

00:07:07.809 --> 00:07:08.228
eighth dimension.

00:07:08.500 --> 00:07:10.180
And this MizMowr opened with a profound

00:07:10.221 --> 00:07:12.002
note where Dowd said everything that I

00:07:12.463 --> 00:07:13.745
have been saying about him

00:07:13.865 --> 00:07:14.605
is that Yahowah

00:07:15.026 --> 00:07:17.689
proved His case that we as people can

00:07:17.809 --> 00:07:21.052
pass muster with God.

00:07:21.072 --> 00:07:22.454
We can be interesting to God.

00:07:22.694 --> 00:07:23.995
We can have intelligent conversation with

00:07:24.519 --> 00:07:27.882
God.

00:07:27.983 --> 00:07:29.103
We can be responsive to God.

00:07:29.163 --> 00:07:30.805
We can engage and make tremendous

00:07:30.846 --> 00:07:33.028
contributions to life with Yahowah.

00:07:33.067 --> 00:07:33.327
If we act like Dowd.

00:07:33.668 --> 00:07:35.170
If we try to emulate his attitude,

00:07:35.189 --> 00:07:37.591
his attributes,

00:07:37.651 --> 00:07:41.836
and focus on what made him so special,

00:07:41.935 --> 00:07:44.237
why God chose him above all others,

00:07:44.576 --> 00:07:48.418
why God fulfilled Pesach, Matsah,

00:07:48.459 --> 00:07:49.738
and Bikuwrym through this man,

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:52.581
opening the doorway to life for us,

00:07:52.620 --> 00:07:54.482
so that we can cross that threshold

00:07:54.541 --> 00:07:56.581
and enter His family and live with Him

00:07:56.601 --> 00:07:57.903
forevermore.

00:07:57.983 --> 00:08:00.603
All of this is because Dowd is the

00:08:00.744 --> 00:08:02.805
exemplar of what God’s trying to achieve

00:08:03.285 --> 00:08:05.607
with us, and he is the one who

00:08:05.646 --> 00:08:06.187
was responsible for reconciling our

00:08:06.846 --> 00:08:09.670
relationship with Yahowah so we can

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:12.353
return and be family again. And so all

00:08:12.374 --> 00:08:14.995
of that is proven

00:08:15.016 --> 00:08:17.699
through the narrative of the sixth MizMowr

00:08:17.740 --> 00:08:20.502
when you understand it.

00:08:20.562 --> 00:08:23.346
And that’s why we have been focusing on

00:08:23.406 --> 00:08:24.447
it.

00:08:25.148 --> 00:08:27.848
We’re about now to start the third

00:08:27.869 --> 00:08:28.848
statement in that profound psalm.

00:08:28.908 --> 00:08:31.250
And this is what Dowd wrote.

00:08:31.490 --> 00:08:35.831
In addition, my soul, my nepesh aniy,

00:08:35.892 --> 00:08:39.052
my consciousness,

00:08:39.633 --> 00:08:42.134
that part of me that animates life and

00:08:43.263 --> 00:08:45.904
enables me to observe my environment and

00:08:45.965 --> 00:08:46.846
to respond, my inner person,

00:08:46.865 --> 00:08:49.028
my personality, my attitude and aptitude,

00:08:49.067 --> 00:08:51.289
along with all of my achievements.

00:08:51.330 --> 00:08:53.650
This is the part that accompanies me into

00:08:53.691 --> 00:08:57.094
all eternity.

00:08:58.095 --> 00:09:00.297
My nepesh is enormously eager and anxious

00:09:01.957 --> 00:09:05.701
about the terrifying agony, the ma’od

00:09:05.880 --> 00:09:06.761
ba’al,

00:09:07.182 --> 00:09:11.525
which is, I’m in a tremendous hurry,

00:09:12.634 --> 00:09:16.437
wanting to hasten the day that this

00:09:16.958 --> 00:09:18.100
alarming anguish is over.

00:09:20.442 --> 00:09:21.484
So You, Yahowah,

00:09:21.524 --> 00:09:24.287
will be the restoring witness.

00:09:24.464 --> 00:09:24.903
You, Yahowah,

00:09:25.845 --> 00:09:28.687
will position the time of the eternal

00:09:28.726 --> 00:09:29.147
testimony to be delivered to show these

00:09:29.187 --> 00:09:32.389
overlapping dates and extend this period

00:09:32.448 --> 00:09:35.692
of witness.

00:09:35.731 --> 00:09:36.971
Yahowah, You and I both want to return.

00:09:36.989 --> 00:09:39.529
You have decided, and I concur,

00:09:39.549 --> 00:09:42.230
that Your desire is to restore.

00:09:42.570 --> 00:09:42.811
This was written as the Piel Imperative,

00:09:42.832 --> 00:09:44.432
Paragoga K, Cohortative.

00:09:44.471 --> 00:09:44.971
Wow, it’s Dowd’s will, Yahowah’s will,

00:09:45.113 --> 00:09:46.472
all passionately blended together

00:09:46.501 --> 00:09:48.473
and emphatically told and emphatically

00:09:48.493 --> 00:09:50.996
stated.

00:09:50.996 --> 00:09:53.201
It is my desire and Your decision to

00:09:53.260 --> 00:09:55.561
deliver salvation with my soul.

00:09:55.582 --> 00:09:58.926
Chalats nepesh ‘any.

00:09:59.066 --> 00:10:00.888
You have chosen to support my choice to

00:10:00.967 --> 00:10:04.110
have You do what is required to rescue

00:10:04.730 --> 00:10:07.033
and withdraw my consciousness and

00:10:08.975 --> 00:10:10.936
therefore to save by what we accomplished

00:10:10.975 --> 00:10:11.376
together in the Piel, Imperative,

00:10:12.116 --> 00:10:14.356
Cohortative, Paragoga K.

00:10:14.417 --> 00:10:17.258
Piel means that Yahowah is the One who,

00:10:17.878 --> 00:10:20.138
as the subject of that sentence,

00:10:20.798 --> 00:10:24.119
is causing the object,

00:10:24.158 --> 00:10:26.919
which is Dowd’s soul,

00:10:27.120 --> 00:10:30.379
to be able to do these things.

00:10:30.399 --> 00:10:32.681
And the Imperative means that this is a

00:10:32.721 --> 00:10:35.361
statement of second-person volition,

00:10:35.381 --> 00:10:37.422
which means it is the person being spoken

00:10:38.336 --> 00:10:41.581
of—You, me,

00:10:41.863 --> 00:10:44.868
and Yahowah’s will to accomplish this.

00:10:45.509 --> 00:10:46.971
The Cohortative means that the speaker in

00:10:47.130 --> 00:10:48.332
first person agrees.

00:10:49.394 --> 00:10:50.517
The Paragoga K says emphatically,

00:10:51.490 --> 00:10:54.753
this is what we want.

00:10:55.053 --> 00:10:57.434
It’s an expression of volition in first

00:10:57.716 --> 00:11:00.017
and second person whereby Yah and Dowd

00:11:00.116 --> 00:11:01.097
agree to save through his soul.

00:11:01.118 --> 00:11:03.279
He goes on to say,

00:11:03.340 --> 00:11:05.860
You want to deliver me, liberating me,

00:11:05.921 --> 00:11:07.302
rescuing and saving through me.

00:11:07.623 --> 00:11:10.585
Yasha’ is the primary verb in the Hebrew

00:11:11.264 --> 00:11:12.186
language, although there are many.

00:11:13.779 --> 00:11:15.321
It is the principal verb in the Hebrew

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.243
language to convey delivering salvation,

00:11:17.302 --> 00:11:19.524
to be victorious,

00:11:20.065 --> 00:11:20.784
to provide for the common good through me.

00:11:21.085 --> 00:11:23.606
Yasha’ ‘any because of the witness that this

00:11:23.725 --> 00:11:24.625
provides to Your enduring love, Your

00:11:26.889 --> 00:11:27.090
unfailing kindness, Your tremendous

00:11:32.219 --> 00:11:33.259
generosity

00:11:33.639 --> 00:11:35.660
and loyal devotion.

00:11:35.701 --> 00:11:37.501
Chesed ‘atah, MizMowr,

00:11:37.542 --> 00:11:38.722
lyrics to sing, Psalm 6:4.

00:11:39.102 --> 00:11:39.682
Wow.

00:11:39.743 --> 00:11:40.844
We have really hit pay dirt here.

00:11:41.203 --> 00:11:43.566
This is,

00:11:43.725 --> 00:11:44.625
I cannot underestimate—or overestimate,

00:11:45.206 --> 00:11:47.128
I should say—

00:11:47.447 --> 00:11:49.668
I cannot overestimate how profoundly

00:11:49.708 --> 00:11:50.950
important all of this is for us to

00:11:51.370 --> 00:11:53.711
appreciate.

00:11:53.751 --> 00:11:56.432
It is complete and total validation of the

00:11:56.452 --> 00:11:57.494
greatest discovery ever made.

00:11:57.994 --> 00:12:00.635
This

00:12:01.673 --> 00:12:06.921
realization that we are at a place where

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:11.207
the seven spirits of Yahowah that have been

00:12:11.307 --> 00:12:13.672
afforded to the Chowter,

00:12:13.851 --> 00:12:14.572
acting as a stem of that tree of

00:12:15.457 --> 00:12:16.458
knowledge,

00:12:17.318 --> 00:12:19.000
is now bearing fruit to the fact that

00:12:19.059 --> 00:12:21.402
Dowd is the One through whom Yahowah

00:12:21.542 --> 00:12:21.782
worked to prove

00:12:21.841 --> 00:12:24.423
that man can be interesting,

00:12:24.464 --> 00:12:24.903
that man can be trustworthy,

00:12:25.845 --> 00:12:28.687
and that it is possible to work through

00:12:28.726 --> 00:12:29.147
men of the right attitude and ambition to

00:12:29.187 --> 00:12:32.389
achieve greatness.

00:12:32.448 --> 00:12:35.692
And that it is Dowd who is the

00:12:35.731 --> 00:12:36.971
Messiah and Son of God,

