00:25:10.080 --> 00:25:12.481
So then Dowd’s soul, enveloped in Yahowah’s

00:25:13.846 --> 00:25:17.407
Ruwach,

00:25:17.468 --> 00:25:19.348
left She’owl and went back to Shamaym to

00:25:19.388 --> 00:25:20.868
be with his Father.

00:25:20.888 --> 00:25:22.769
And it is Dowd’s nepesh soul that is

00:25:22.809 --> 00:25:25.869
going to be put into a rather remarkable

00:25:25.890 --> 00:25:26.431
basar body upon his return just eight

00:25:26.471 --> 00:25:28.451
years from now on Yowm Kipurym,

00:25:28.471 --> 00:25:30.151
the great homecoming.

00:25:30.852 --> 00:25:32.432
And it’s going to be a glorious sight.

00:25:32.491 --> 00:25:34.873
But it’s his soul.

00:25:34.952 --> 00:25:35.712
And it’s your soul that you should care

00:25:37.881 --> 00:25:39.763
about.

00:25:39.784 --> 00:25:41.365
This begins by saying that his soul is

00:25:41.826 --> 00:25:44.369
both eager and anxious, as it should be,

00:25:44.410 --> 00:25:45.451
as you would expect it to be,

00:25:46.011 --> 00:25:48.275
about the terrifying agony.

00:25:48.315 --> 00:25:49.717
Imagine that Dowd is one of two people

00:25:50.017 --> 00:25:51.077
that figured out,

00:25:51.117 --> 00:25:52.760
based upon Yahowah’s testimony,

00:25:52.780 --> 00:25:53.501
that his body at one point would serve

00:25:54.201 --> 00:25:57.624
as the sacrifice and that his soul would

00:25:57.683 --> 00:26:00.905
redeem his people.

00:26:01.306 --> 00:26:03.307
And that he knew, having read the Towrah,

00:26:03.846 --> 00:26:06.307
that it was appropriate for him to

00:26:06.348 --> 00:26:07.909
volunteer to serve as the Pesach ‘Ayil.

00:26:07.929 --> 00:26:08.950
And that for him to volunteer to carry

00:26:09.069 --> 00:26:10.109
our guilt into She’owl,

00:26:10.130 --> 00:26:13.551
to have it burden his soul,

00:26:13.571 --> 00:26:15.833
so he would actually have his soul be

00:26:15.873 --> 00:26:18.134
incarcerated in She’owl during Matsah.

00:26:18.154 --> 00:26:21.797
And yes,

00:26:21.856 --> 00:26:22.277
he was enormously eager to do this because

00:26:23.279 --> 00:26:26.501
he knew of all of the good it

00:26:26.521 --> 00:26:27.241
would do.

00:26:27.721 --> 00:26:29.623
Please his Father, it would cause his

00:26:29.663 --> 00:26:32.384
people to respect him at long last, and

00:26:32.424 --> 00:26:35.566
it would cause everyone who is ultimately

00:26:35.605 --> 00:26:38.607
part of the Covenant Family to receive the

00:26:39.087 --> 00:26:39.989
benefits of the Covenant based upon what

00:26:41.048 --> 00:26:42.369
Dowd would achieve. But he was also anxious

00:26:43.430 --> 00:26:44.171
because crucifixion and the torment that

00:26:45.250 --> 00:26:46.471
Dowd received based upon the beast of Rome

00:26:46.491 --> 00:26:46.692
prior to it and then the journey into

00:26:49.519 --> 00:26:52.421
She’owl was terrifying.

00:26:52.601 --> 00:26:56.001
He wrote about it, so it was going

00:26:56.342 --> 00:26:57.922
to be horribly anguishing, and he told

00:26:58.662 --> 00:26:59.942
us all about it. And he had to

00:27:02.222 --> 00:27:06.263
write about it. That’s why the

00:27:08.184 --> 00:27:09.184
twenty-second and the eighty-eighth MizMowr

00:27:09.464 --> 00:27:11.066
exist. And so he knew he was

00:27:13.066 --> 00:27:16.727
at that point a thousand years away from

00:27:16.767 --> 00:27:19.028
fulfilling it. He was anguished. He had seen

00:27:21.453 --> 00:27:22.193
it as a prophet. He knew what he

00:27:24.315 --> 00:27:27.375
was going to do and he knew what

00:27:28.435 --> 00:27:29.655
was going to happen, but he said, “Yep,

00:27:29.675 --> 00:27:32.136
I’m in it. I’m committed. I’m going to

00:27:33.096 --> 00:27:35.157
do it.”

00:27:36.096 --> 00:27:38.298
I said he was one of two.

00:27:38.338 --> 00:27:40.618
We did a family show where one of

00:27:40.679 --> 00:27:42.460
my long-term favorite people,

00:27:42.500 --> 00:27:44.381
good friend for well over a score of

00:27:44.621 --> 00:27:47.461
years, asked me,

00:27:47.500 --> 00:27:48.902
“How does it feel knowing that you’re going

00:27:48.922 --> 00:27:49.221
to be the other?”

00:27:50.559 --> 00:27:53.201
And it is.

00:27:53.260 --> 00:27:55.561
The story that Yahowah has written for the

00:27:55.582 --> 00:28:00.523
role that I have been asked to play

00:28:00.663 --> 00:28:03.365
is that I am the ‘Adamah Parah.

00:28:03.404 --> 00:28:05.204
I’m the one who will be sacrificed on

00:28:05.345 --> 00:28:08.665
Taruw’ah, and it’s going to be gruesome.

00:28:09.227 --> 00:28:12.968
Prophets have spoken of it, and it’s a

00:28:12.988 --> 00:28:15.169
mauling, and I’m mauled by the same beast.

00:28:15.209 --> 00:28:17.130
Donald Trump and Satan are trying to

00:28:17.170 --> 00:28:18.470
establish the fourth Reich,

00:28:19.445 --> 00:28:21.426
the fourth rise of all things Rome.

00:28:21.467 --> 00:28:25.468
It’s why he makes the declaration on the

00:28:25.508 --> 00:28:27.048
Ides of March,

00:28:27.088 --> 00:28:28.309
which is so politically and religiously

00:28:28.349 --> 00:28:30.009
symbolic in Rome, that he is God.

00:28:30.049 --> 00:28:34.231
And three years after that,

00:28:34.291 --> 00:28:36.073
we’re going to have our rendezvous, and I’m

00:28:36.113 --> 00:28:37.772
going to have the mal’ak that have

00:28:37.813 --> 00:28:38.953
protected me stand down. The Ruwach that

00:28:38.973 --> 00:28:40.013
have been so essential to what I have

00:28:40.034 --> 00:28:41.555
learned and can share will step aside for

00:28:41.914 --> 00:28:46.096
the moment, and my physical body will be

00:28:46.136 --> 00:28:46.336
bludgeoned. Now my soul will survive it

00:28:47.113 --> 00:28:48.473
just like Dowd’s soul did as well. And

00:28:48.493 --> 00:28:50.996
while I’m eager

00:28:51.016 --> 00:28:53.417
to get at it and to do what

00:28:53.678 --> 00:28:57.099
God wants done,

00:28:57.160 --> 00:28:58.721
knowing all the benefit because it purges

00:28:58.921 --> 00:29:00.082
the mortal remnant of Yisra’el

00:29:00.102 --> 00:29:00.563
so they can witness the homecoming,

00:29:01.143 --> 00:29:01.784
the family reunion,

00:29:02.463 --> 00:29:04.586
and then enter the restoration of Gan

00:29:04.625 --> 00:29:05.987
‘Eden, the Garden of ‘Eden,

00:29:06.106 --> 00:29:07.567
as the entire Earth is transformed into

00:29:08.106 --> 00:29:10.416
that condition.

00:29:10.436 --> 00:29:11.117
And we have the opportunity to teach these

00:29:11.157 --> 00:29:14.340
people how to engage with God,

00:29:14.420 --> 00:29:15.641
how to be trustworthy around God,

00:29:15.701 --> 00:29:16.621
how to listen and be observant and learn.

00:29:17.523 --> 00:29:19.724
The fact of the matter is I’m also

00:29:19.764 --> 00:29:20.844
a little anxious about it because, well,

00:29:20.864 --> 00:29:23.047
you know,

00:29:23.588 --> 00:29:24.288
it’s not going to be a pleasant

00:29:24.989 --> 00:29:26.449
experience,

00:29:27.610 --> 00:29:30.351
although the aftermath will be.

00:29:31.652 --> 00:29:32.652
So this is what Dowd is speaking of

00:29:34.012 --> 00:29:36.034
here.

00:29:37.715 --> 00:29:38.614
It’s just another affirmation of what

00:29:38.675 --> 00:29:39.956
we’re saying is true.

00:29:39.976 --> 00:29:42.277
So You, Yahowah,

00:29:42.748 --> 00:29:43.289
will commence the restoring witness.

00:29:44.168 --> 00:29:45.548
‘Atah ‘ad matseh.

00:29:45.789 --> 00:29:46.849
Meanwhile, in consideration for this,

00:29:47.489 --> 00:29:49.269
in the duration of time,

00:29:49.849 --> 00:29:52.990
the eternal testimony will show the

00:29:54.710 --> 00:29:57.152
overlapping dates and extended period.

00:29:57.311 --> 00:30:00.253
MizMowr 6:3.

00:30:00.293 --> 00:30:00.894
Yes.

00:30:00.954 --> 00:30:03.396
Well, Dowd did his part.

00:30:03.456 --> 00:30:07.739
He lived a life exemplary of what God

00:30:07.940 --> 00:30:08.820
wants from us.

00:30:09.221 --> 00:30:12.244
He wasn’t perfect because perfect would be

00:30:12.284 --> 00:30:12.784
boring.

00:30:14.065 --> 00:30:17.106
He was interesting.

00:30:17.186 --> 00:30:20.170
He didn’t know all things,

00:30:20.250 --> 00:30:22.751
but he learned many things.

00:30:24.539 --> 00:30:26.041
He came to understand.

00:30:26.161 --> 00:30:29.643
He made mistakes.

00:30:29.682 --> 00:30:29.923
He got up.

00:30:31.505 --> 00:30:34.306
He dusted himself off and charged ahead

00:30:34.367 --> 00:30:37.389
again, wiser for the experience,

00:30:37.548 --> 00:30:41.411
more trustworthy for having acknowledged

00:30:41.451 --> 00:30:42.052
that he had goofed and knew what needed

00:30:43.775 --> 00:30:48.802
to be accomplished.

00:30:48.902 --> 00:30:49.963
He could be relied upon to fulfill Pesach,

00:30:50.264 --> 00:30:52.987
Matsah, and Bikuwrym.

00:30:53.027 --> 00:30:54.710
He did so

00:30:55.190 --> 00:30:56.353
two thousand years ago.

00:30:57.385 --> 00:31:00.809
As such,

00:31:01.528 --> 00:31:02.650
he is God’s implement through whom He is

00:31:02.730 --> 00:31:04.831
going to work with us through eternity.

00:31:08.355 --> 00:31:10.416
God delegates everything.

00:31:11.157 --> 00:31:14.340
Everything He does is through those He has

00:31:14.420 --> 00:31:15.641
chosen to work with.

00:31:15.701 --> 00:31:16.621
It’s His ‘ebed.

00:31:17.523 --> 00:31:19.724
Dowd is Yahowah’s ‘ebed, His coworker.

00:31:20.349 --> 00:31:23.551
But while all of that is true,

00:31:23.592 --> 00:31:25.773
and while it is profoundly important,

00:31:26.013 --> 00:31:27.875
until I was introduced to it,

00:31:30.006 --> 00:31:31.707
could prove it,

00:31:32.367 --> 00:31:32.867
share that evidence with you,

00:31:33.488 --> 00:31:34.929
no one knew it.

00:31:36.369 --> 00:31:36.891
And if you don’t know it,

00:31:38.551 --> 00:31:39.251
it doesn’t do any good.

00:31:39.271 --> 00:31:40.053
The Chowter that is inspired to do these

00:31:41.394 --> 00:31:43.694
things,

00:31:43.734 --> 00:31:43.996
that is a stem whose roots

00:31:44.036 --> 00:31:46.017
anchor him in a forthright position,

00:31:48.097 --> 00:31:51.741
who is parah, productive, as the ‘etsah,

00:31:52.422 --> 00:31:56.866
this counsel on the complete story

00:31:56.906 --> 00:31:58.949
relative to da’ath, knowledge,

00:31:59.549 --> 00:32:02.071
infused as he has been with the Spirit

00:32:03.373 --> 00:32:05.756
of Yahowah, the Spirit of chakmah,

00:32:05.776 --> 00:32:07.998
intelligence, the Spirit of biynah,

00:32:08.038 --> 00:32:09.740
understanding,

00:32:10.339 --> 00:32:11.080
all buttressed with the Spirit of geburah,

00:32:12.090 --> 00:32:15.453
strength of conviction and confidence,

00:32:15.653 --> 00:32:17.816
such as to rekindle a respect for Yahowah.

00:32:18.676 --> 00:32:23.099
And he does so by coming to appreciate

00:32:24.862 --> 00:32:26.863
this role between Father and Son.

00:32:26.903 --> 00:32:28.724
And so without the commencement of the

00:32:30.219 --> 00:32:32.259
restoring witness,

00:32:32.299 --> 00:32:33.160
without the consideration of this

00:32:33.599 --> 00:32:35.381
timeline,

00:32:35.461 --> 00:32:36.040
me giving you the exact dates that Dowd

00:32:36.560 --> 00:32:38.662
fulfilled Pesach, Matsah,

00:32:38.701 --> 00:32:40.021
and Bikuwrym in 33 CE

00:32:40.061 --> 00:32:41.942
and explaining how that was year four

00:32:42.002 --> 00:32:45.183
thousand Yah

00:32:45.223 --> 00:32:45.624
and precisely when in year six thousand

00:32:45.644 --> 00:32:45.943
Yah

00:32:46.084 --> 00:32:48.325
we’re going to witness the fulfillment of

00:32:48.365 --> 00:32:48.605
Taruw’ah, Kipurym, and Sukah,

00:32:49.924 --> 00:32:51.685
and what each of those dates represent and

00:32:52.627 --> 00:32:54.729
how you can capitalize upon them and who

00:32:55.108 --> 00:32:57.949
the players are that have been foretold

00:32:58.349 --> 00:33:01.529
from the beginning that will make this

00:33:01.569 --> 00:33:03.530
happen.

00:33:03.570 --> 00:33:05.551
Without all of that coming forth from the

00:33:05.592 --> 00:33:05.912
restoring witness,

00:33:05.932 --> 00:33:09.213
no one benefits from it.

00:33:11.413 --> 00:33:12.293
The harvests don’t occur.

00:33:14.693 --> 00:33:15.614
The homecoming is canceled.

00:33:16.235 --> 00:33:17.954
Earth is destroyed as opposed to being

00:33:19.251 --> 00:33:21.012
returned to the conditions that were

00:33:21.172 --> 00:33:23.675
experienced in ‘Eden. And so it is quite

00:33:23.695 --> 00:33:28.438
clear—excuse me, our dogs are very

00:33:28.597 --> 00:33:39.105
happy when they have this opportunity

00:33:39.125 --> 00:33:41.585
to celebrate with whoever may be

00:33:41.646 --> 00:33:44.568
visiting, so…

00:33:44.789 --> 00:33:46.889
Dowd is a man who loves Yahowah and

00:33:46.909 --> 00:33:48.280
cherishes His name.

00:33:48.280 --> 00:33:50.280
And you can see he repeatedly uses it.

00:33:50.280 --> 00:33:52.280
And that’s a clue.

00:33:52.280 --> 00:33:54.280
This is the man that Yahowah chose.

00:33:54.280 --> 00:33:56.280
He said this is the man that He

00:33:56.280 --> 00:33:58.280
dearly loves.

00:33:58.280 --> 00:34:00.280
He explained that Dowd had characteristics

00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:02.280
and attributes that made him very special

00:34:02.280 --> 00:34:04.280
in Yahowah’s eyes and different from the

00:34:04.280 --> 00:34:06.280
reasons that men would choose other men.

00:34:06.280 --> 00:34:08.280
God said that he is the Chosen One.

00:34:08.280 --> 00:34:10.280
He is the One that God chose to

00:34:10.280 --> 00:34:12.280
anoint as Mashyach, not once,

00:34:12.280 --> 00:34:14.280
but three times.

00:34:14.280 --> 00:34:16.280
He’s the only man that God said,

00:34:16.280 --> 00:34:18.280
“He is My Son; I am His Father.”

00:34:18.280 --> 00:34:20.280
And he is the man that God chose

00:34:20.280 --> 00:34:22.280
to fulfill the most important dates in

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:24.280
human history—Pesach, Matsah,

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:26.280
and Bikuwrym.

00:34:26.280 --> 00:34:28.280
And all of this is so that Father

00:34:28.280 --> 00:34:30.280
and Son can return.

00:34:30.280 --> 00:34:32.280
So we read here, Yahowah,

00:34:32.280 --> 00:34:34.280
You and I both want You to return.

00:34:34.280 --> 00:34:36.280
God can’t return until His people return

00:34:36.280 --> 00:34:38.280
to Him.

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:40.280
God says this over and over again,

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:42.280
beginning in the Towrah,

00:34:42.280 --> 00:34:44.280
running all the way through the prophets.

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:46.280
And Howsha’ is just emphatic.

00:34:46.280 --> 00:34:48.280
He says that he is leaving Yisra’el.

00:34:48.280 --> 00:34:50.280
It’s a divorce.

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:52.280
The divorce was for religious infidelity

00:34:52.280 --> 00:34:54.280
and that He will not return until His

00:34:54.280 --> 00:34:56.280
people return to Him,

00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:58.280
which is the reason we’re doing these

00:34:58.280 --> 00:35:00.280
programs,

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:02.280
trying to get your attention so that you

00:35:02.280 --> 00:35:04.280
know what God is offering and what you

00:35:04.280 --> 00:35:06.280
need to do to return to Him so

00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:08.280
that He will return to you.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:10.280
And so this is what Dowd wants.

00:35:10.280 --> 00:35:12.280
He wants Yahowah to return.

00:35:12.280 --> 00:35:14.280
When Yahowah returns, Dowd returns.

00:35:14.280 --> 00:35:16.280
When Yahowah returns,

00:35:16.280 --> 00:35:18.280
their relationship is reconciled.

00:35:18.280 --> 00:35:20.280
When Dowd returns,

00:35:20.280 --> 00:35:22.280
we get the second shot at ‘Eden.

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:24.280
And so the Dowd is the master of

00:35:24.280 --> 00:35:26.280
the Imperative and the Cohortative.

00:35:26.280 --> 00:35:28.280
You’ve heard me probably on these programs

00:35:28.280 --> 00:35:30.280
talk about Hebrew grammar and my love for

00:35:30.280 --> 00:35:32.280
it.

00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:34.280
But there are aspects of Hebrew grammar

00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:36.280
that are just different than anybody else

00:35:36.280 --> 00:35:38.280
or any other language.

00:35:38.280 --> 00:35:40.280
One of those things is the ability to

00:35:40.280 --> 00:35:42.280
convey volition, choice, will,

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:44.280
desire in first and second person.

00:35:44.280 --> 00:35:46.280
The Imperative is an expression of second

00:35:46.280 --> 00:35:48.280
person volition.

00:35:48.280 --> 00:35:50.280
The Cohortative conveys first person

00:35:50.280 --> 00:35:52.280
volition.

00:35:52.280 --> 00:35:54.280
So by writing a statement, speaking of

00:35:54.280 --> 00:35:56.280
Dowd, speaking for Yahowah,

00:35:56.280 --> 00:35:58.280
saying “You want to,” it’s Yahowah.

00:35:58.280 --> 00:36:00.280
In the Imperfect, in the Imperative,

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:02.280
excuse me, it’s saying that, God,

00:36:02.280 --> 00:36:04.280
this is what You want to do.

00:36:04.280 --> 00:36:06.280
I know Your will,

00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:08.280
and You’ve made this decision.

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:10.280
And in the Cohortative, it’s saying,

00:36:10.280 --> 00:36:12.280
I agree.

00:36:12.280 --> 00:36:14.280
It’s the same decision I’ve made.

00:36:14.280 --> 00:36:16.280
We want the same thing.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:18.280
And the Paragoga K say,

00:36:18.280 --> 00:36:20.280
this is not only true, it’s emphatic.

00:36:20.280 --> 00:36:22.280
And the Piel says, I understand, Yahowah,

00:36:22.280 --> 00:36:24.280
that You’re going to enable this through

00:36:24.280 --> 00:36:26.280
my soul,

00:36:26.280 --> 00:36:28.280
that You as the subject are going to

00:36:28.280 --> 00:36:30.280
cause this to happen based upon the object

00:36:30.280 --> 00:36:32.280
of the verb,

00:36:32.280 --> 00:36:34.280
which is chalats being the object being

00:36:34.280 --> 00:36:36.280
nephesh.

00:36:36.280 --> 00:36:38.280
God, it is my desire and Your decision.

00:36:38.280 --> 00:36:40.280
We are of like mind regarding delivering

00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:42.280
salvation with my soul.

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:44.280
I don’t know how I could make it

00:36:44.280 --> 00:36:46.280
or God could make it any clearer for

00:36:46.280 --> 00:36:48.280
you.

00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:50.280
You have chosen to support my choice to

00:36:50.280 --> 00:36:52.280
have You do what is required to rescue

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:54.280
and withdraw with me and through my

00:36:54.280 --> 00:36:56.280
consciousness.

00:36:56.280 --> 00:36:58.280
It is Dowd’s soul that will exist three,

